### **SCENE 6: FIRST DAY â€” THE OXYGEN BAZAAR**

**INT. OXYGEN BAZAAR â€” DAY**

*Overwhelming. Loud. Crowded. Hundreds of Martians buying, selling, shouting in Tharsic.*

**Kai (now age 7, one year later) follows Sera through the crowd. He's wearing ill-fitting Martian clothes. He moves SLOWLYâ€”the "Heavy Air" effect in full force (48fps slowed to 24fps).**

**Other children run past him, moving in "normal" speed. They laugh. Point.**

**CHILD 1**  
(In Tharsic)  
*Look! Thin-lung walks like stone!*

**CHILD 2**  
*Maybe he'll fall and crack!*

**They mimic his slow movements. Laughter.**

**Kai tries to speed up. Stumbles. Falls.**

**The crowd parts around him. No one helps.**

**Sera appears. Pulls him up.**

**SERA**  
(In Tharsic, to the children)  
