(Smiles)  
That's what Mars teaches. Try. Fail. Try again. Until you don't fail.

**Kai waters the plants carefully. One of them has a tiny green tomato, no bigger than his thumbnail.**

**KAI**  
(Whispers to the plant)  
Don't die. Please.

**SERA**  
(Watching)  
*Mali'shka*, plants don't listen to words. They listen to care.

