(Tears fall)  
Please wake up. Please.

**The machines beep. Slower. Slower.**

**Then: a long, flat tone.**

**Kai doesn't move. Just stares at her face, reflected in the cracked glass.**

**CAMERA:** Extreme close-up on the cracked windowâ€”Kai's face fragmented into dozens of pieces.

**FADE TO BLACK.**

**END ACT ONE.**

